The canonical guide for this repo is **[AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md)** — read it for full structure, commands, and architecture.

Key rules:

-   Bun is the package manager and runtime (not npm). Dev server: port 4001.
-   Conventional Commits, bare types, subject only. Prettier: 4-space, single quotes, semicolons, 100-col.
-   Section geometry is stored in **PDF points (72 DPI)**, never CSS pixels.
-   Use the `docmosaic.*` Tailwind design tokens, not raw hex.
-   Keep the PDF byte-diff guard green: `packages/core/src/pdf/generate.test.ts`.
-   Two published packages — `@docmosaic/core`, `@docmosaic/react`. Add a changeset (`bun run changeset`) for package-affecting changes.

@AGENTS.md
